the **Resolution Calulator**'s **Multiplier** to **2** which will take the **Input Image Dimensions**, multiplies it by **2** and passes it to the Upscale Image **Width** and **Height** parammeters.\n\nFinally, set the self-explanatory parameters of the **Tiled Sampler** and **run** the **Workflow**.\n\n---\n\n## Important!\n\n---\n\nDo **NOT** use **Mute** on Upscaler / Resizer! Enable or Bypass only.\n\n---\n\nThe **Multiplier** is applied to the **original** Input Image dimensions. With **Multiplier** set to **2**, You'll double the original image size regardless of what Upscale Model You're using if Resizer is enabled. When the Resizer is Bypassed, the Multiplier does nothing.\n\n---\n\n## Color Codes\n\n### Red Nodes\n\nNormally **Loaders** and things You **need** to change for Your specific setup **before** First Use\n\n---\n\n### Purple Nodes\n\nThings You probably **will** interact with the most\n\n---\n\n### Blue Nodes\n\nGenerally just **stet it and forget it** nodes that You'll set once\n\n---\n\n### Black Nodes\nYou don't ever really need to touch those\n"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":8,"type":"JohnsPromptLibrary","pos":[960,30],"size":[400,500],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"Clip","localized_name":"Clip","name":"Clip","shape":7,"type":"CLIP","link":6},{"localized_name":"category","name":"category","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"category"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"title","name":"title","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"title"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"prompt","name":"prompt","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"prompt"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"negative","name":"negative","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"negative"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"Prompt Conditioning","name":"Prompt Conditioning","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[13]},{"localized_name":"Negative Conditioning","name":"Negative Conditioning","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[14]},{"localized_name":"Prompt Text","nam